high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the stove on the left.
Pick up the pot on the right side of the stove.
Turn around and go to the right, go forward to the brown shelf on the right.
Put the pot on the right side of the second shelf.
Turn to the right and go to the counter just past the stove on the left.
Pick up the pot that is on the counter.
Turn to the left and go to forward to the brown shelf on the right.
Put the pot on the second shelf to the left of the other pot.
anns.task_desc: Put two pots on a shelf.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the stove.
Pick up the pan from the right front burner.
Carry the pan to the brown shelving unit in the corner to the left of the counter.
Place the pan on the second shelf.
Move back to stand at the counter between the stove and sink.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Return to the brown shelving unit while carrying the pan.
Place the pan on the second shelf to the left of the one you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two pans to a shelf to the left of the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and take about three steps then turn left to face the stove.
Take the pot off of the front right burner.
Take several steps to your left to face the shelves that are to the left of the counter in front of you.
Put the pot towards the right of the second shelf from the bottom.
Turn right and walk to the sink then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the pot that's in front of you.
Walk back to where you put the first pot.
Put this pot to the left of the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put two pots on a shelf.
